        <td>
            <img src="<%=Url.Content("~/images/desktop/preview/ch7/p359.jpg")  %>">
        </td>
        <td>The tunnel removal appears to be the first and only removal of an underwater vehicular crossing in the United States. The bridge contractor won the removal contract with a $17.5 million bid, $4.3 million less than the next lowest bid. Williams Brothers cut the tunnel into sections and recycled the concrete for use in other road construction projects. 	

        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
