        <td>
            <img src="<%=Url.Content("~/images/desktop/preview/ch7/p361.jpg")  %>">
        </td>
        <td>In 2001, after two serious collisions with ocean vessels, the Loop 610 bridge may have finally earned a well-deserved reputation as being a bridge too low.
        </td>
