            <img src="<%=Url.Content("~/images/desktop/preview/ch7/p371.jpg")  %>">
        </td>
        <td>The advance of bridge-building technology that has made so many bridges around the world feasible may make even the most marginal of projects, such as the Galveston-Bolivar crossing, a reality.			
